== 合一運動 ==
巴關發起的運動使用了各種名稱，<ref name="RA"/>像是黃金紀元基金會、薄伽梵法教、迦樂季法教，以及合一組織。<ref name="RA"/>印度媒體也稱之為'''迦樂季教派'''。<ref name="indiatoday.intoday"/><ref name="Hindu2008">{{cite news | last = Special Correspondent | first = | work = The Hindu | title = Kalki, Amma Bhagavan cut-outs set on fire |date = 2008-04-26 }} [http://www.hindu.com/2008/04/26/stories/2008042659020400.htm Kalki, Amma Bhagavan cut-outs set on fire] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hindu.com/2008/04/26/stories/2008042659020400.htm |date=20131101162605 }}</ref>

該運動始於80年代初期，據報截至2008年為止，全球已有超過1千四百萬名信眾，<ref name="ET_Mumbai">{{cite news | last = TNN | work = Economic Times | title = 孟買公司學'''合一''' | date = 2008-02-02 }}[http://articles.economictimes.indiatimes.com/2008-02-02/news/27736762_1_jagdish-capoor-bse-top-guns (economictimes.com)] {{Wayback|url=http://articles.economictimes.indiatimes.com/2008-02-02/news/27736762_1_jagdish-capoor-bse-top-guns |date=20160305041633 }}</ref>並表示它的使命是「幫所有人創造合一，延續靈性轉化。」<ref name="ET_Mumbai"/>它的儀式包括給予'''滴夏'''。<ref name="deeksha"/><ref name="RA"/>

合一運動的總部和阿施藍<ref name="ashram"/>主堂均位處印度[[安得拉邦|安得拉邦]]的{{link-en|Varadaiahpalem|Varadaiahpalem}}。<ref name="RA"/>阿施藍中有{{link-en|合一大殿|Oneness Temple}}，建造成本估計有7,500萬美元，據說內有亞洲最大的內部無柱式靜心殿。
